               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18451215-name-759" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18451215-name-759" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18451215-name-759" type="surname" value="JONES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18451215-name-759" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN JONES</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the service of George Peppercorn, a butcher, in Broadway, Deptford. On Friday, the 12th of Dec, about three o'clock in the afternoon, I saw the prisoner take a piece of beef off the block in the shop, and put it under her shawl—I knew her before, and am sure she is the person—there was no one else in the shop—I called Grace—we went after her, and brought her back—she took the beef from under her shawl, and asked Grace to forgive her.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
